OL,3,CCaptain did 'absolutely nothing' to
OL,4,Cstop fatal tanker crash, jury told
OL,6,FThe captain of a container ship
OL,7,Finvolved in a fatal crash in the North
OL,8,FSea did "absolutely nothing" to avoid
OL,9,Fthe collision, a court has heard.
OL,11,FRussian Vladimir Motin was in charge
OL,12,Fof the Solong when it hit the anchored
OL,13,FUS oil tanker Stena Immaculate off the
OL,14,FEast Yorkshire coast on 10 March last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FFilipino crewman Angelo Pernia, 38,
OL,18,Fdied in the incident.
