OL,3,CCaptain did 'absolutely nothing' to
OL,4,Cstop fatal tanker crash, jury told
OL,6,FMr Motin, 59, of Primorsky, St
OL,7,FPetersburg, is on trial at the Old
OL,8,FBailey accused of manslaughter by
OL,9,Fgross negligence.
OL,11,FOpening the prosecution case on
OL,12,FTuesday afternoon, Tom Little KC said
OL,13,Fthe case involved the "entirely
OL,14,Favoidable death of a seaman" who would
OL,15,F"still be alive if it was not for the
OL,16,Fgrossly negligent conduct of the man
OL,17,Fin the dock".
