OL,3,CCaptain did 'absolutely nothing' to
OL,4,Cstop fatal tanker crash, jury told
OL,6,FHe told the court the collision, which
OL,7,Fcaused a huge explosion, happened
OL,8,Fclose to the Humber Estuary. The Stena
OL,9,FImmaculate was carrying "very large
OL,10,Fquantities of aviation fuel" when it
OL,11,Fwas hit by the Solong.
OL,13,FMr Little said: "Despite an obvious
OL,14,Fcollision course, the defendant did
OL,15,Fnot deviate his vessel from its path
OL,16,Fand the impending catastrophe that lay
OL,17,Fahead.
