OL,3,CCaptain did 'absolutely nothing' to
OL,4,Cstop fatal tanker crash, jury told
OL,6,F"The defendant was responsible for
OL,7,Fnavigating the ship, not only because
OL,8,Fhe was the captain but because he was
OL,9,Fon sole watch duty at the time and
OL,10,Fultimately he did nothing, absolutely
OL,11,Fnothing, to avoid the collision."
OL,13,FThe prosecutor said the location of
OL,14,Fthe Stena Immaculate would have been
OL,15,Fvisible on the Solong's radar display
OL,16,Faround 36 minutes before the vessels
OL,17,Fcollided.
